9.Write a Java program to find whether an array is sorted or not.
class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int[] arr = {1, 2, 3, 4, 5};

        boolean sorted = true;

        // Check if array is sorted
        for(int i = 0; i < arr.length - 1; i++) {

            if(arr[i] > arr[i + 1]) {

                sorted = false;
                break;
            }
        }

        if(sorted)
            System.out.println("Array is sorted");
        else
            System.out.println("Array is not sorted");
    }
}
Output
Array is sorted
